CallerIsNotNewPotentialOwner().details: Revert with an error when attempting to claim ownership of the      contract with a caller that is not the current potential owner.

CallerIsNotOwner().details: Revert with an error when attempting to call a function with the      onlyOwner modifier from an account other than that of the owner.

InitialOwnerIsNullAddress().details: Revert with an error when attempting to register an initial owner      and supplying the null address.

NewPotentialOwnerIsNullAddress().details: Revert with an error when attempting to register a new potential      owner and supplying the null address.

OwnerAlreadySet(address).details: Revert with an error when attempting to set an initial owner when      one has already been set.

OwnershipTransferred(address,address).details: Emit an event whenever contract ownership is transferred.

params.newOwner: The new owner of the contract.
params.previousOwner: The previous owner of the contract.

PotentialOwnerUpdated(address).details: Emit an event whenever the contract owner registers a new potential      owner.

params.newPotentialOwner: The new potential owner of the contract.

returns._0: The address of the potential owner.

params.newPotentialOwner: The address for which to initiate ownership                          transfer to.
